Package: rmaven
Title: Run Java Build Tool Maven From R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Robert", "Challen", , "rob@terminological.co.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Running Maven from R allows for better integration of Java libraries into R. Maven provides various options for resolving complied Java code dependencies, configuring classpaths, or compiling Java source code, all of which are needed for efficient use of Java within R.
